(26, 1, '2009-10-04 10:13:48', '2009-10-04 17:13:48', '<p style="text-align: left;">Flip Foundry is a design, web development, application and hardware development company.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><!--more--></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://localhost/flipfoundry/?attachment_id=165" rel="attachment wp-att-165"><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-165" alt="longimage6" src="http://localhost/flipfoundry/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/longimage6.jpg" width="628" height="79" /></a></h3>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;"></h3>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">We Are An Agile Development Team</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Everything starts with an idea. Whether it is our own idea or something new and exciting brought to us by a client, we immediately get to work on creating a real live application. In fact, rapid development and deployment is our primary service. We have experience in the rapid actualization of new and innovative ideas into a living, breathing business. We achieve this through a balanced but broad spectrum of capabilities, ranging from accomplished, business designers, communication and interface designers, developers who cross multiple boundaries of typical programming environments, inventors who thrive on developing next-generation innovations, and a very powerful framework to back it all up.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">A Powerful Custom Framework</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We have developed a framework that is the culmination of all our professional experiences. Our framework is immediately capable of supporting an enormous amount of user traffic, handling in-depth social networking features, communicating with external devices, and deploying a suite of applications associated with any new web platform we might come up with.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">A Passion for Excellence and Evolution</h3>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">We are perfectionists. We feel that you deserve no less than the most finely-polished application anyone can produce. We strive to place ourselves at the cutting edge of the newest web technologies. We don''t just do this for our clients - we do this for ourselves. Because we are inventors and businessmen first, and we are passionate about creating new products, services and ideas.</p>', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'services-2', '', '', '2013-01-20 21:57:23', '2013-01-20 21:57:23', '', 0, 'http://pixelcraft.makedesignnotwar.com/themes/wp/mu/wpmu/?page_id=26', 2, 'page', '', 0),
(1318, 1, '2013-01-20 21:52:59', '2013-01-20 21:52:59', 'Flip Foundry is a design, web development, application and hardware development company.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-165" style="margin: 40px 0;" title="longimage6" alt="longimage6" src="http://localhost/flipfoundry/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/longimage6.jpg" width="628" height="79" />\r\n<h3>An Agile Team</h3>\r\nEverything starts with an idea. Whether it is our own idea or something new and exciting brought to us by a client, we immediately get to work on creating a real live application. In fact, rapid development and deployment is our primary service. We have experience in the rapid actualization of new and innovative ideas into a living, breathing business. We achieve this through a balanced but broad spectrum of capabilities, ranging from accomplished, business designers, communication and interface designers, developers who cross multiple boundaries of typical programming environments, inventors who thrive on developing next-generation innovations, and a very powerful framework to back it all up.\r\n<h3>A Powerful Custom Framework</h3>\r\nWe have developed a framework that is the culmination of all our professional experiences. Our framework is immediately capable of supporting an enormous amount of user traffic, handling in-depth social networking features, communicating with external devices, and deploying a suite of applications associated with any new web platform we might come up with.\r\n<h3>A Passion for Excellence and Evolution</h3>\r\nWe are perfectionists. We feel that you deserve no less than the most finely-polished application anyone can produce. We strive to place ourselves at the cutting edge of the newest web technologies. We don''t just do this for our clients - we do this for ourselves. Because we are inventors and businessmen first, and we are passionate about creating new products, services and ideas.', 'Services', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', 